node.text: Tough one to take on Saturday. Unfortunately we just fell short but I’m proud of all of the boys and the effort everyone has put in over the last few weeks. Thank you so much for your support. We’ll be back and we’ll do everything we can to make the nation proud 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁷󠁬󠁳󠁿❤️ #TogetherStronger
